Sorry to hear that. You're correct that we didn't need his testimony. 
From: 
Sent: Monday, November 30, 2020 9:51 AM 
To 
Subject: Efrain Reyes 
ust learned from Probation that Efrain Reyes died. It sounds like it was in his sleep. Given his history, I 
think it may have been drug related, but perhaps not. Either way, my recollection is that you didn't expect to need him for 
anything Epstein/MCC-related, but just want to keep you in the loop in case my memory is wrong. 
Assistant United States Attorney 
Southern District of New York 
EFTA00019925
